Step back in time with our exquisite Framed Print of "King Frederick William III and Queen Louise of Prussia in the company of the family of Count von Schaffgotsch on the Schneekoppe, August 1800" by Knotel, published by Bridgeman Images. This stunning color lithograph transports you to the regal era of Prussia, showcasing the royal family in their finest attire, surrounded by their esteemed guests atop the Schneekoppe mountain. Add an air of sophistication and history to any room with this beautiful and authentic work of art.
